cial. You can use the arrangement of trees to find hiding places to shoot from, and should watch out for CPU soldiers also doing so.","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/cannon-fodder--1","videos":[{"id":53775,"game":42335,"name":"Gameplay Video","video_id":"4jvG4K5oeeM","checksum":"2847a964-0390-d17c-8fab-30ca2c65e2e0"}]}